{
  "spec": "Holo Dock (ADR-0059) is the native-feel bottom dock/taskbar: it ADOPTS the zebar widget-pack schema (holo-zpack-schema.json) and the TranslucentTB accent-state model (holo-translucenttb-accents.json) as byte-pinned, content-addressed κ-objects and renders natively — no foreign runtime (ADR-0029). It is golden-ratio-proportioned (holo-phi), OS-adaptive (HoloPlatform → data-holo-platform), glass-translucent (--holo-glass-* tokens), linked to Holo UI/UX, and editable like every other substrate object; the dock config validates against the adopted schema.",
  "authority": "zebar (github.com/glzr-io/zebar — resources/zpack-schema.json) · TranslucentTB (github.com/TranslucentTB/TranslucentTB — settings.schema.json) · ADR-0029 (adopt OSS desktop standards as κ-objects, never run a foreign runtime) · ADR-0030 (Holo UI) · ADR-0057 (readability floor) · W3C CSS backdrop-filter / Color 4 light-dark() / Custom Properties · golden ratio (φ) · verify by static analysis of the served chrome",
  "witnessed": false,
  "covers": [
    "holo-dock",
    "glass",
    "phi-sizing",
    "os-adaptive",
    "zpack-adopt",
    "translucenttb-adopt",
    "a11y",
    "conformance"
  ],
  "schemaPin": "sha256:3556d024a5e320c864845bf1afcef7d893620357cd8183798ebd9bd3f17fc454",
  "checks": {
    "file present + non-empty: holo-dock.js": true,
    "file present + non-empty: holo-dock.css": true,
    "file present + non-empty: holo-dock-config.json": true,
    "file present + non-empty: holo-zpack-schema.json": true,
    "file present + non-empty: holo-translucenttb-accents.json": true,
    "dock config is a valid instance of the vendored zebar zpack schema": true,
    "zpack schema carries the faithful dockToEdge.edge enum [top,right,bottom,left]": true,
    "holo-theme.css declares the glass token --holo-glass-blur": true,
    "holo-theme.css declares the glass token --holo-glass-acrylic-fx": true,
    "holo-theme.css declares the glass token --holo-glass-opaque-bg": true,
    "holo-theme.css declares the glass token --holo-glass-clear-bg": true,
    "holo-theme.css declares the glass token --holo-glass-tint": true,
    "holo-dock.css sizes off holo-phi tokens (--holo-size-* / --holo-phi)": true,
    "holo-dock.css uses no raw px for height/gap (φ tokens only; ≤2px hairlines/indicators ok)": false,
    "dock styles the windows variant ([data-holo-platform=\"windows\"])": true,
    "dock styles the macos variant ([data-holo-platform=\"macos\"])": true,
    "dock styles the ios variant ([data-holo-platform=\"ios\"])": true,
    "dock styles the ipados variant ([data-holo-platform=\"ipados\"])": true,
    "dock styles the android variant ([data-holo-platform=\"android\"])": true,
    "dock styles the linux variant ([data-holo-platform=\"linux\"])": true,
    "dock styles the chromeos variant ([data-holo-platform=\"chromeos\"])": true,
    "holo-dock.js stamps data-holo-platform from HoloPlatform.profileFor": true,
    "dock styles both orientations ([data-orient=\"bottom\"] + [data-orient=\"left\"])": true,
    "holo-dock.js switches orientation on the fullscreen state": true,
    "home.html links holo-dock.css": true,
    "home.html loads holo-dock.js": true,
    "home.html hides the dock behind the boot splash": true,
    "no sub-16px font-size in the dock CSS/JS": true,
    "translucenttb accent model is faithfully adopted (5 states + blur_radius 0–750 /3 + token map)": true
  },
  "rawPx": [
    "250: gap:6px",
    "300: gap:6px",
    "462: height:18px"
  ],
